title: Globočdol
data: Globočdol (pronounced [ɡlɔˈboːtʃdɔu̯]) is a small settlement in the Municipality of Mirna Peč in southeastern Slovenia. The area is part of the historical region of Lower Carniola and is now included in the Southeast Slovenia Statistical Region.[2] This article about the Municipality of Mirna Peč in Slovenia is a stub.
